        <abstract> 
<p>Has enjoyed reading LA’s book [<hi rend="italic">Études sur les glaciers</hi> (1840)].</p>  
<p>Hopes LA will pardon manner in which CD has alluded to his work on glaciers in his <hi rend="italic">Journal of researches</hi>, of which he sends a copy.</p> 
